WEBVTT

00:08.006 --> 00:10.442
DOUGLAS, WILL YOU
PLEASE PASS THE CATSUP?

00:10.543 --> 00:11.943
THE WHAT?

00:12.011 --> 00:13.979
THE CATSUP.

00:17.550 --> 00:19.784
YOU MEAN THE KETCHUP?

00:21.420 --> 00:25.623
EDUCATED PEOPLE
PRONOUNCE IT CATSUP.

00:25.691 --> 00:28.560
NOT IF THEY WANT ME
TO PASS IT TO THEM.

00:28.644 --> 00:30.495
FINE. IF THAT'S THE WAY
YOU'RE GOING TO BE,

00:30.563 --> 00:31.963
THEN I'LL DO WITHOUT.

00:33.900 --> 00:35.266
NOT GONNA HAPPEN,
OLD MAN.

00:35.334 --> 00:36.500
MY BURGER'S
GETTING COLD.

00:36.568 --> 00:37.769
JUST GIVE ME
THE CATSUP!

00:37.837 --> 00:39.137
OK, IT'S CALLED KETCHUP.

00:39.205 --> 00:41.106
SAY IT RIGHT AND YOU CAN HAVE IT. NO.

00:41.173 --> 00:43.074
SAY IT. SAY IT. NO.

00:43.159 --> 00:44.108
I WILL
NEVER SAY IT.

00:44.176 --> 00:47.278
I'D RATHER DIE
THAN SAY IT.

00:47.330 --> 00:49.598
THEN SHE'S
STAYING OVER HERE.

00:49.665 --> 00:52.867
ME LLAMO KETCHUP.

00:52.868 --> 00:54.369
FINE.

00:54.436 --> 00:56.371
THEN JUST SAY
GOOD-BYE TO THESE.

00:56.438 --> 00:57.972
AHH!

00:58.091 --> 00:59.240
WHY YOU GOTTA DO THAT?

00:59.308 --> 01:00.976
YOU WANT THE CATSUP,
YOU CAN HAVE THE CATSUP.

01:01.043 --> 01:02.643
HERE. GOD.

01:05.047 --> 01:05.981
THANK YOU.
THAT'S ENOUGH.

01:06.048 --> 01:07.148
OK, GOOD.

01:07.216 --> 01:08.233
THAT'S ENOUGH.

01:08.301 --> 01:10.435
THAT'S ENOUGH.
THAT'S ENOUGH.

01:10.503 --> 01:11.769
THAT'S ENOUGH!

01:11.837 --> 01:12.521
OH, IS THAT ENOUGH?

01:12.588 --> 01:13.904
YES, THAT'S ENOUGH.
THAT'S ENOUGH.

01:13.972 --> 01:15.673
THAN SAY IT!
SAY-SAY IT!

01:15.741 --> 01:17.275
WHAT?
SAY WHAT?!

01:17.343 --> 01:18.410
WHAT'S IT CALLED?!

01:18.478 --> 01:20.745
KETCHUP!

01:24.516 --> 01:27.585
AND THAT'S HOW WE LEARN.

